comment: The builder for creating {@link ExecuteAppFunctionRequest} instances.

methods.name: public Builder setParameters(@NonNull GenericDocument parameters)
methods.comment:
* Sets parameters for invoking the app function. Within this {@link GenericDocument}, the
         * property names are the names of the function parameters and the property values are the
         * values of those parameters. Defaults to an empty {@link GenericDocument} if not set.

methods.name: public Builder setExtras(@NonNull Bundle extras)
methods.comment:
* Sets the additional metadata relevant to this function execution request. Defaults to an
         * empty {@link Bundle} if not set.

methods.name: public ExecuteAppFunctionRequest build()
methods.comment: Constructs a new {@link ExecuteAppFunctionRequest} from the contents of this builder.
